                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "C’est Pierrot, Pierrot, Pierrot.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "CE n’est pas Pierrot en herbe\nNon plus que Pierrot en gerbe.\nC’est Pierrot, Pierrot, Pierrot.\nPierrot gamin, Pierrot gosse,\nLe cerneau hors de la cosse,\nC’est Pierrot, Pierrot, Pierrot."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Bien qu’un rien plus haut qu’un mètre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Le mignon drôle sait mettre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Dans ses yeux l’éclair d’acier",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Qui sied au subtil génie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "De sa malice finie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "De poète-grimacier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bien qu’un rien plus haut qu’un mètre,\nLe mignon drôle sait mettre\nDans ses yeux l’éclair d’acier\nQui sied au subtil génie\nDe sa malice finie\nDe poète-grimacier."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Lèvres rouge-de-blessure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Où sommeille la luxure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Face pâle aux rictus fins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Longue, très accentuée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Qu’on dirait habituée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "A contempler toutes fins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Lèvres rouge-de-blessure\nOù sommeille la luxure,\nFace pâle aux rictus fins,\nLongue, très accentuée\nQu’on dirait habituée\nA contempler toutes fins,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Corps fluet et non pas maigre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Voix de fille et non pas aigre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Corps d’éphèbe en tout petit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Voix de tête, corps en fête,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Créature toujours prête",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "A soûler chaque appétit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Corps fluet et non pas maigre,\nVoix de fille et non pas aigre,\nCorps d’éphèbe en tout petit,\nVoix de tête, corps en fête,\nCréature toujours prête\nA soûler chaque appétit."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Va, frère, va, camarade,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Fais le diable, bats l’estrade",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Dans ton rêve et sur Paris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Et par le monde, et sois l’âme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Vile, haute, noble, infâme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "De nos innocents esprits !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Va, frère, va, camarade,\nFais le diable, bats l’estrade\nDans ton rêve et sur Paris\nEt par le monde, et sois l’âme\nVile, haute, noble, infâme\nDe nos innocents esprits !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Grandis, car c’est la coutume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Cube ta riche amertume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Exagère ta gaieté",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Caricature, auréole,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "La grimace et le symbole",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "De notre simplicité !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Grandis, car c’est la coutume,\nCube ta riche amertume,\nExagère ta gaieté\nCaricature, auréole,\nLa grimace et le symbole\nDe notre simplicité !"
